!  please note:  these two files--~4Dgifts/{.Xdefaults_1280,.Xdefaults_1024}--
!  are taken directly from the demos account which is (obviously) where they 
!  were written to go.  it was decided to keep explicit copies in ~4Dgifts for 
!  those users who don't load the demos subsystems.  while the applications 
!  are all other than those built under 4Dgifts, it is felt that the 
!  existence/structure of these resolution/size/screen-specific files as yet
!  another "example" is useful and informative.
!
